      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has some noticeable clear coat peeling on the hood and roof, along with a few minor door dings and scratches typical for its year. Inside, the upholstery shows some wear and there is a small crack in the dashboard, but all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car is sound and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some suspension work in the near future. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at an affordable price point.",
