    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional daily driver at an accessible price point. The engine and transmission are fully operational, though you should expect some visible cosmetic wear on both the interior upholstery and the exterior paint. While it has been maintained to keep it running safely, there may be some minor non-essential repairs or maintenance items due soon. This car is perfect for someone who prioritizes utility and reliability over a flawless aesthetic.",
