      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains exceptional compression across all six cylinders, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the installation of treated rod bearings and a comprehensive reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to mitigate floor pan fatigue. The drivetrain features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and precise shift gates. Handling is sharpened by refreshed bushings and a limited-slip differential that remains tight under load. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the chassis dynamics and powertrain performance remain at a high standard for the discerning driver.",
